{
  "id": "adv_bond_chs_01_03",
  "title": "白石千紗3",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_karaokeroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "karaokeroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_03-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "カラオケ、久しぶりだな～\nえへへ、何から歌おうかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Karaoke‚ it's been a while~\nEhehe‚ where should I start?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_karaokeroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "karaokeroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 7.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_03-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "他の人の歌を歌える機会って、なかなかない、よね\n非公式だけど、今日はカバーし放題",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's rare‚ to get chance to sing other people's songs‚ isn't it?\nIt's unofficial‚ but today I'm going to cover as many songs as I want",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_karaokeroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "karaokeroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 16.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_03-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "雫ちゃんの歌をいっぱい聴けるのも、贅沢かも\nあ、悩んじゃってるから、先に入れていいよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Being able to listen to Shizuku's songs a lot‚ might be a luxury\nAh‚ I'm having trouble deciding‚ you can go ahead and sing it",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_karaokeroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "karaokeroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 24.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_03-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあ、遠慮なく……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well then‚ without any hesitation…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_karaokeroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "karaokeroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 27.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_03-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "わ～、スリクスさんの『So What?』\n雫ちゃんが歌うとこんな感じなんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow~‚ ⅢX-san's \"So What?\"\nThis is what it feels like when Shizuku sings",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.6999994914,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_karaokeroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "karaokeroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 36.566666158
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_03-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "千紗ちゃんの『恋と花火』も、凄く良かった\n……次、たぶん知らない曲だけど、大丈夫？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa's \"Love and Fireworks\"‚ was also really good\n…Next‚ you probably don't know this song‚ is that okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.566666158,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_karaokeroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "karaokeroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.866666158
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_03-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "うん。雫ちゃんが好きな曲、聴いてみたいな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. I'd like to hear a song Shizuku likes",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.866666158,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_karaokeroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "karaokeroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 49.7333328247
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_03-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあ、『ピアニッシモで大丈夫？』の新曲\n『チーズDeキッス』……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then‚\"Is It Okay to Pianissimo?\"'s new song\n\"Cheese De Kiss\"…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.7333328247,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_karaokeroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "karaokeroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 55.166666158
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_03-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "はい、チーズ、それキッス\nとろけるようなアイウォンチュー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hi‚ cheese‚ that's a kiss\nFeel like melting‚ I want youー",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.166666158,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_karaokeroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "karaokeroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 62.566666158
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_03-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、雫ちゃん、すっごく可愛かったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe‚ Shizuku-chan‚ you were so cute",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.5666656494,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_karaokeroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "karaokeroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 67.7666656494
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_03-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃんの好きなアイドルの曲だから\n私もちっちゃく歌っちゃった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's an idol song that saki-chan likes‚\nso I sang it a little‚ too",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.7666656494,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_karaokeroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "karaokeroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 73.1999989827
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_03-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "え……それなら、デュエットすれば良かった……\n千紗ちゃんが歌ったら、絶対可愛いのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh… In that case‚ we should have done a duet…\nIt would definitely be cute if Chisa-chan sang it",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.1999989827,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_karaokeroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "karaokeroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 80.8333323161
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_03-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうかな……？　雫ちゃんみたいに\n思い切って歌えたらいいんだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "R-Really…? I wish\nI could sing it as boldly as Shizuku-chan…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.8333323161,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_karaokeroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "karaokeroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 88.1999989827
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_03-szk007.m4a",
      "text": "私しか聴いてないから、大丈夫\n間違えちゃっても、誰も怒らない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's okay‚ I'm the only one listening\nEven if you make a mistake‚ no one gets angry",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.1999989827,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_karaokeroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "karaokeroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 93.7666656494
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_03-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ……思い切って私も歌うね\n雫ちゃんも、知ってたら入ってきてね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then… I'll go ahead and sing it‚ too\nShizuku-chan‚ if you know it‚ please join in",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.7666656494,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_karaokeroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "karaokeroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 101.9999989827
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_03-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "――『とこやみ手毬唄』",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――\"Tokoyami Temari Uta\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.9999989827,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_karaokeroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "karaokeroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 103.9999989827
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_03-chs010.m4a",
      "text": "ひと～り、やっては父のため～……\nふた～り、やっては母のため～……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "One~‚ do it for my father~…\nTwo~‚ do it for my mother~…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.9999989827,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_karaokeroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "karaokeroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 115.0999989827
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_03-chs011.m4a",
      "text": "落ち武者さーまのおなーりじゃー……\n突き刺せ、沈めろ、狩りつくせ～……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fallen samurai-san has arrivedー…\nStab‚ sink‚ hunt them all~…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.0999989827,
